These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, lemonade, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, dahlia, iris
House: craftsman, farmhouse, gothic-revival, wooden
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, green, pink, aquamarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, collecting, filmmaking
 1. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
 3. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
 4. the person who growslily is the person who likes green##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 6. the person who likes green is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 7. the person who likes pink is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 8. the person who likes pink is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
11. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
13. the wooden house is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
14. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
15. the person who likes green is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5
16. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | juice     | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Flower        | zinnia  | lily | dahlia      | iris      |
| House         | wooden  | farmhouse    | gothic-revival | craftsman       |
| Color       | coral | green   | pink      | aquamarine  |
| Hobby   | drawing      | magic-tricks  | collecting   | filmmaking      |

