 8. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
10. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
11. the person who likes amber is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
13. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
14. the person playing poker is the modern house##1
15. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the person who likes ebony##8
16. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person playing snooker##8
17. the person playing whist is the craftsman house##1
18. the craftsman house is not the person driving the car##6
19. the victorian house is not the person playing canasta##6
20. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
21. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5

